| Size | Value | Margin | Padding |
|------|-------|--------|---------|
| 0 | 0 | `cfl-m-0` | `cfl-p-0` |
| 1 | 0.25rem | `cfl-m-1` | `cfl-p-1` |
| 2 | 0.5rem | `cfl-m-2` | `cfl-p-2` |
| 3 | 1rem | `cfl-m-3` | `cfl-p-3` |
